    • printMaze

      public void printMaze()
      Prints a visual representation of the maze to the console. The representation includes rooms, halls, treasures, challenges, and entry points. Rooms are displayed as boxes with symbols indicating their contents: - '*' for treasure rooms - '?' for enigma challenges - '@' for lever challenges - '#' for entry rooms Halls are represented as lines connecting the rooms.
